node.text: With everything that had happened she really thought I was gonna miss her special day for the 1st time but I’d rather spend eternity in hell before I let her down. @vannah I’m not the best father but I try to do my best for you & long as you let me know when I’m messing up I promise you I’ll always be there & show you how a man supposed to treat a queen. Here’s some clips of her surprise party stay tuned for the full one on her YouTube dropping next week!!! Enjoy cause we bout to flood the streets with our life #MyEverything #PrincessVannah
